<div class="p">Adopted Indian, Asian girls oppressed:</div>
<div class="p">The male chumps mass, contribute small remarks,
<div class="p">Discover purpose when their lady barks,
<div class="p">And fall in line to kick their father's corpse.
<div class="p">With drawling tones, these miniature Thorpes
<div class="p">Confess to crimes committed April last,
