<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The Whirl, the Whirlâ€”where did those sweet years go?</div>
<div class="p">Nobody knows where time's smooth currents flow.</div>
<div class="p">But good times, bad times; frenzied study, lax;</div>
<div class="p">Sweep Freshmen toward their odyssey's climax.</div>
<div class="p">A well-adjusted young adult begowned</div>
<div class="p">Appears with learning's foursquare headgear crowned;</div>
<div class="p">He takes life's dancing reigns with debt and knowledge,</div>
<div class="p">And blusters his descendants off to college.</div>
